==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exterritoriality
<hw>Ex*ter`ri*to`ri*al"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>The state of being beyond the limits of a country.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being free from the jurisdiction of a
country when within its territorial limits.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extersion</ent>⟦br⟧
